---
title: Teriyaki Plant-Based Mince & Broccoli Stir-Fry with Ginger Rice
description: It doesn’t get much more simple and delicious than this plant-based mince and broccoli stir-fry. Our teriyaki sauce is the perfect addition, bringing tonnes of flavour in just one ingredient. Don’t forget the fragrant rice - the subtle heat of our punchy ginger paste adds an aromatic twist. No need to wait, dig in while it’s hot!

